oleil.</p>\n        <a href=\"/products/smart-watch-2-0\" style=\"color:var(--black); font-size:12px; font-weight:700; text-decoration:underline;\">En savoir plus</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"grid-item\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0850/9571/0986/files/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-03_at_22.37.43.jpg?v=1775248715\" class=\"grid-img\" alt=\"Autonomie\">\n        <h2 class=\"grid-title\">7 jours d'autonomie</h2>\n        <p class=\"grid-text\">Oubliez le chargeur. Performance longue durée garantie.</p>\n        <a href=\"/products/smart-watch-2-0\" style=\"color:var(--black); font-size:12px; font-weight:700; text-decoration:underline;\">Commander</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"split-section\">\n    <div>\n      <h2 class=\"split-title\">Profitez de l'offre <span class=\"accent-color\">−50%</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom:30px; opacity:0.8;\">Valable uniquement aujourd'hui pour les nouveaux clients.</p>\n    </div>\n    <a href=\"/products/smart-watch-2-0\" class=\"primary-btn\" style=\"background:var(--accent);\">Obtenir la mienne</a>\n  </section>\n\n  <footer class=\"custom-footer\">\n    © 2026 IA High Tec Shop — Design Minimaliste\n  </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n\n{% endif %}",
